Package cetus.transforms

Class NormalizeReturn

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.transforms.TransformPass
      • cetus.transforms.ProcedureTransformPass
        • cetus.transforms.NormalizeReturn
  • public class NormalizeReturn
extends ProcedureTransformPass
    This normalization pass is intended to simplify return statements for the Procedures in the program. Return statements with no return expressions are added at the end of the procedure if a return statement doesn't exist already. For all return statements in the procedure, the return expressions are assigned to a standard return variable and are replaced in the return statement with this standard return variable. Especially useful for statement based analyses and simplification of interprocedural analyses.
